MM16DRead - Status reader program for MM16D device
---------------------------------------------------

1. About software
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
  You can check status of MM16D growing house controllers with this
software via network.

The package includes a GUI application and three command-line scripts.
Everything can be queried with the GUI program. With the scripts only
the measured data in different format (CSV, JSON, TXT and XML) and
protocol (HTTP, Modbus/TCP). 

The 'wget' program required for the 'mm16dread-http' script to work can
be found in all Linux distributions, install it with the package manager.
The 'modpoll' program required for 'mm16dread-modbus-tcp' scripts to work
can be downloaded from <https://www.modbusdriver.com/modpoll.html>.

2. How to get installer package for my OS?
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
a. Visit homepage (see later) to download installer packages:

  architecture  operation system        filename
  ---------------------------------------------------------------
  (all)         (source code)           mm16dread-0.1.tar.gz
  (all)         FreeBSD port            mm16dread-0.1-FreeBSD-Port.shar
  i386          FreeBSD                 mm16dread-0.1.txz
  i386          Debian GNU/Linux        mm16dread_0.1-1_i386.deb
  amd64         Linux                   mm16dread-0.1-amd64.bin
  amd64         Linux                   mm16dread-0.1-amd64.tar.gz
  i586          Linux                   mm16dread-0.1-i586.bin
  i586          Linux                   mm16dread-0.1-i586.tar.gz
  i586          Windows 32 bit          mm16dread-0.1-win32.exe
  i586          Windows 32 bit          mm16dread-0.1-win32.msi
  i586          Windows 32 bit          mm16dread-0.1-win32.zip

b. Download from Github

  $ git clone https://github.com/pozsarzs/mm16dread.git

c. Download from Debian repository

  set reporitory:
  # echo "deb http://www.pozsarzs.hu/deb/ ./" >> /etc/apt/sources.list
  # wget -q -O - http://www.pozsarzs.hu/deb/KEY.gpg | apt-key add -
  # apt-get update

  install
  # apt-get install mm16dread

